**Your field should not be called `isCurrent` in the first place.** *Is* is a verb and verbs are inappropriate to represent an Object&#39;s state. Use an adjective instead, and suddenly your getter / setter names will make more sense:


    private boolean current;

    public boolean isCurrent(){
        return current;
    }

    public void setCurrent(final boolean current){
        this.current = current;
    }

